additional_info:
もっと縮めたい場合、以下の width 値を調節する。
#cw_outer_west,
#cw_leftmenu {
  width: 179px !important; /* (239px - 60px) */
}
#cw_roomlist_items_area .ui_roomlist_view .ui_room_title {
  width: 97px; /* (157px - 60px) */
}

css:
@-moz-document domain("www.chatwork.com") {
#cw_roomfilter {
  -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
  -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
  -ms-box-sizing: border-box;
  -o-box-sizing: border-box;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  width: 100%;
}
#cw_roomfilter_area .ui_roomcategory_area {
  overflow: hidden;
}
#cw_roomcategory {
  float: none;
  width: auto;
  overflow: hidden;
}
#cw_outer_west,
#cw_leftmenu {
  width: 179px !important; /* (239px - 60px) */
}
#cw_roomlist_items_area .ui_roomlist_view .ui_room_title {
  width: 97px; /* (157px - 60px) */
}
#cw_outer_center {
  left: 180px !important;
}
}
